{"tid":2240283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拜登：「試試自己的乳房，但感覺永遠不夠」","createTime":"2020-10-12T14:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T03:49:44.000Z","uid":184679,"like":330,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"159b9c0b9fe77d24a140345732078eb2cbd78008","tid":2240283,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:17:55.000Z","msg":"美國總統大選即將到來，各黨卯足全力替自己拉選票，民主黨候選人拜登（Joe Biden）於美國時間10日到賓夕法尼亞州拜票時，卻疑似說錯話，提到「試試自己的乳房，但感覺永遠不夠」，讓網友紛紛傻眼，狂轟他演說時、腦袋到底裝些什麼？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kfh8zC86CIzqEVFoEDdmtA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM1NC4xMzMzMzMzMzMzMzMz/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/0B2rrVJAbT06M4h3Yn8Lbw--~B/aD00MTU7dz03NTA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/setn.com.tw/8fefbe81a0581b33d473aeb4a23c5447\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fkfh8zC86CIzqEVFoEDdmtA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM1NC4xMzMzMzMzMzMzMzMz%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F0B2rrVJAbT06M4h3Yn8Lbw--~B%2FaD00MTU7dz03NTA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F8fefbe81a0581b33d473aeb4a23c5447&h=6fb83077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖／翻攝自Joe Biden臉書）<br />\n<br />\n拜登在拜票時，先是提及川普2016年承諾的基礎設施計劃沒做到，接著就表示如果他當選了，會改善勞工階級的生活，沒想到下一秒他拋出的一段話，瞬間震驚全場，「每個地方都有同樣故事，你正試試自己的乳房（You are trying your breast），但感覺永遠不夠，你不是在尋求救贖，只是在尋找公平機會」。<br />\n<br />\n拜登口誤的影片曝光後，立刻流傳於網路，雖然大家認為拜登應該是要說「你正努力做到最好（Trying your best）」，仍有不少網友砲轟，留言表示，「是不是要去治療痴呆症了」、「我想知道為甚麼他在過去47年沒有試過胸部」、「拜登是不是在觀眾席裡看到豐滿女子，才會腦子和嘴巴不同步」、「很顯然，拜登在精神上沒有能力擔任總統」。<br />\n<br />\n面對沸沸揚揚的討論，拜登至今沒正面回應，不過今日仍在自己臉書發文，「當川普被告知每天有1000名美國人死於新冠狀病毒時，他聳肩地說『就是這樣』，但真的是這樣嗎？這個總統根本不關心他發誓要服務的美國人，這真的很可恥！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/嗆川普承諾跳票-拜登竟說試試胸部-133055104.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E5%97%86%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE%E8%B7%B3%E7%A5%A8-%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E7%AB%9F%E8%AA%AA%E8%A9%A6%E8%A9%A6%E8%83%B8%E9%83%A8-133055104.html&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V4c%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=bf9160f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/嗆川普承諾跳票-拜登竟說試試胸部-133055104.html</a>"},{"pid":"2b34413900e106a09c3f7997918158ceefffe906","tid":2240283,"uid":9394,"like":531,"dislike":4,"score":527,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:19:47.000Z","msg":"搓my breast <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國人都可以講錯呢啲英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eba8c66fc2ccd58897820b5e56d9ddd25a0c93b","tid":2240283,"uid":140335,"like":469,"dislike":0,"score":469,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:20:12.000Z","msg":"佢向陳克勤致敬"},{"pid":"3037442f4f7db7c8f72c1aeb6a58b26e58e1e3c0","tid":2240283,"uid":137704,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:20:42.000Z","msg":"但繼續投登"},{"pid":"f47e3ac5d9e180bf6472520f9afb8ca3a5b96074","tid":2240283,"uid":28068,"like":163,"dislike":0,"score":163,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:21:16.000Z","msg":"民建聯行得太前<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202396088fe3b1dc68092ce369a66b83166ff562","tid":2240283,"uid":370061,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:21:44.000Z","msg":"真.支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963584a4d742edb9ceff8dd6835db92c5985d4f8","tid":2240283,"uid":358542,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"7eba8c66fc2ccd58897820b5e56d9ddd25a0c93b","tid":2240283,"uid":140335,"like":469,"dislike":0,"score":469,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:20:12.000Z","msg":"佢向陳克勤致敬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:21:51.000Z","msg":"第一時間都係諗起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57cce2b87402bfb3835ac0a5b87b9c108a832011","tid":2240283,"uid":392,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:22:10.000Z